<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Sectors</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Healthcare</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Healthcare buildings can't switch off — theatres, wards and plant rooms run around the clock, and the people inside depend on them. We bring MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works together under one accountable team, so works land safely in live clinical settings, hold to HTM and HBN standards, and keep patients protected throughout.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Healthcare →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">Across every trade</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Four service lines,<br>under one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>HVAC &amp; HTM 03-01 ventilation</li><li>Water hygiene &amp; HTM 04-01 control</li><li>Resilient power &amp; standby supplies</li><li>Medical gas &amp; plant servicing</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Clinical &amp; consulting room fit-out</li><li>Partitions &amp; hygienic wall finishes</li><li>Infection-control-aware works</li><li>Fire-stopping &amp; compartmentation</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Envelope repair &amp; weatherproofing</li><li>Roofing &amp; flat-roof renewal</li><li>Glazing &amp; access upgrades</li><li>Thermal upgrades to Part L</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Ambulance &amp; emergency access</li><li>Car parks &amp; accessible parking</li><li>Therapeutic &amp; green space</li><li>Paths, boundaries &amp; wayfinding</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What matters</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Built around your<br>building.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Built around live, clinical settings</span></h4><ul><li>24/7 occupied, working environments</li><li>Infection control to HBN &amp; HTM</li><li>Phased works around clinical hours</li><li>Isolations, permits &amp; strict controls</li><li>Minimal disruption to patient care</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Compliance, handled</span></h4><ul><li>HTM 03-01 ventilation in healthcare</li><li>HTM 04-01 water &amp; legionella control</li><li>Relevant HBN design guidance</li><li>CDM 2015 throughout the works</li><li>Building Regs Part B &amp; BS 7671</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work in a live, occupied hospital or clinic?</summary><p>Yes. Most healthcare projects are phased around a working building — out-of-hours isolations, temporary services and ward-by-ward handover — so clinical care continues while we work.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you understand HTM and HBN healthcare standards?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver to the Health Technical Memoranda and Health Building Notes that govern healthcare estates, including HTM 03-01 for ventilation and HTM 04-01 for water, with documentation to match.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do you handle infection control during works?</summary><p>We plan works around infection-control requirements from the start — dust and barrier management, agreed permits and isolations, and close coordination with estates and clinical teams to protect patients throughout.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover water hygiene and legionella compliance?</summary><p>Yes. We work to HTM 04-01 for water systems and legionella control, covering safe delivery, flushing regimes and the records the estate needs for ongoing compliance.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span class="ol-nm">MEPH</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial Fit-out</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Landscaping</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compliance &amp; BSA</a></div></div></div></section></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{@site.url}}/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Sectors", "item": "{{@site.url}}/sectors/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Healthcare", "item": "{{@site.url}}/sectors/healthcare/"}]}</script><script typ